    "result": {"data":{"strapiPost":{"strapiId":5370,"title":"Southern Living Named Bentonville On List Of Top Southern Destinations    ","topic":"Highlight","slug":"southern-living-named-bentonville-on-list-of-top-southern-destinations","coverImage":{"publicURL":"/static/7d4e9f331219bebdc67dab67f433ca9f/f61a1d16b2d9114377295a556c552e66.JPG"},"photoCredit":"NWA Daily","date":"2022-11-23","content":"<p>Southern culture magazine, <a href=\"https://www.southernliving.com/trips-to-take-next-year-6825193\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\"><em>Southern Living</em></a>, made a list of top destinations to consider when planning trips for the new year, and Bentonville made the list.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Naturally</strong>: Referring to Bentonville as an “artsy city with an outdoor soul”, the article highlighted the region’s mountain biking opportunities, <a href=\"https://crystalbridges.org/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\">Crystal Bridges Museum of American Art</a>, and <a href=\"https://themomentary.org/?gclid=Cj0KCQiA4OybBhCzARIsAIcfn9mXv_Pxb-wmCOisZ4tGEB8nHXuxhK96WekXqj9WSQR-ph2oCE0H64AaAtYyEALw_wcB\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\">The Momentary</a>.&nbsp;</li><li><strong>For the foodies</strong>: Travelers with an appetite will love the area's budding culinary scene, particularly Bentonville's three <a href=\"https://www.jamesbeard.org/awards\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">2022 James Beard Semifinalists</a>: <a href=\"https://www.thehivebentonville.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\">The Hive</a>, <a href=\"https://www.thepreachersson.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\">The Preacher’s Son</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.yeyosnwa.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\">Yeyo’s</a>.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Find the full list of destinations <a href=\"https://www.southernliving.com/trips-to-take-next-year-6825193\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(220, 161, 13);\">HERE</a>.&nbsp;</p>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"southern-living-named-bentonville-on-list-of-top-southern-destinations"}},
